  "Description": {
    "English": "Ancient words are carved into this <span class=\"name name-stellar\">living document</span>. They read:<br><br>'Now with every storm we beg to be chosen;<br>Arms to the sky, faces to the dirt, calling out with all we have!<br>When heavy raindrops hit the earth, the veins of Atlas answer.<br>The rapture of our consumption is beyond words.'",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "这份<span class=\"name name-stellar\">活经文</span>上刻着古老的文字。上面写道：<br><br>“每当风暴声响起，吾等都乞求被选召；<br>手伸天空，脸面尘土，声嘶力竭！<br>待到磅礴大雨洗刷大地，阿特拉斯的血脉终于回应。<br>吾等消逝时的狂喜溢于言表。”",
    "TraditionalChinese": "被刻進<span class=\"name name-stellar\">活體文件</span>的古老文字。上頭刻著：<br><br>「每當風暴降臨，我們便乞求成為天選之人；<br>手伸天空，臉面塵土，我們聲嘶力竭地呼喚！<br>當強雨擊打地面，寰宇血脈將會回應。<br>我們被吞噬時的狂歡難以言喻。」"
  },
